     <property name="text">
      <string>&lt;html&gt;&lt;head/&gt;&lt;body&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Guess Game&lt;/b&gt; creates a hangman-style game for your Twitch chat. Viewers type &lt;b&gt;!guess &amp;lt;letter/word&amp;gt;&lt;/b&gt; to play.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Templates:&lt;/b&gt; twitchbot_guess.txt, twitchbot_mypoints.txt (customize in templates folder)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;OBS Integration:&lt;/span&gt; Use &lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Export for OBS&lt;/span&gt; from the system tray menu to generate a scene collection that includes Guess Game scenes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;WNP Guess Game&lt;/span&gt; — full game overlay with leaderboard displays&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;WNP Guess Game Basic&lt;/span&gt; — simplified overlay for smaller stream layouts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Online Board:&lt;/b&gt; https://whatsnowplaying.com/guessgame/(your-twitch-username) (requires Charts API key)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
